道我现在毫无能力，但我至少可以劳动。我是没有任何时间会浪费的，我每天每时每刻都在学习。」 据媒体报道，吴谢宇舅舅和姑父已经原谅了吴谢宇，并且签署了谅解书，希望司法机关能够宽大处理。8 月 27 日，吴谢宇姑父对媒体说，他还是希望吴谢宇能够活下来，如果吴谢宇选择上诉，他会全力支持。「弑母者」吴谢宇已正式提起上诉，此前一审被判处死刑"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-05757852ec16318160fe5dd93db6b393_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "97 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485103365"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2ISvz8+f/5YXEAMaCDcwMDgyNTg1IIu814kGMAQ4dUAXcgk0ODUxMDMzNjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1630984093.9935844", "card_id": "Q_481357620", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价任嘉伦、白鹿主演的电视剧《一生一世》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-77840865f1080a62dfc65385c53f3130_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481357620"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "知乎评分 7.8", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2ISvz8+f/5YXEAMaCDY5MjUwMDY4INOrgYkGMAA4SEAYcgk0ODEzNTc2MjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1630984093.9940183", "card_id": "Q_484990362", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "从《青簪行》到《余生请多指教》，杨紫是不是实惨？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "来自粉丝的问题补充（非原题主）： 众所周知杨紫从未说自己惨，粉丝也从未且也不敢说杨紫惨。黑子一边说杨紫真惨，一边说她惨什么惨活该等等 别唱双簧了，烦"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-459664e691288afa2ec6eb503bd45907_qhd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484990362"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2ISvz8+f/5YXEAMaCDcwMDU3NDk4IPfs1YkGMAI4NkAZcgk0ODQ5OTAzNjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="